Introduction

Fu Yaning is a Chinese rapper, singer, and dancer under Gramarie Entertainment. She was a contestant on Girls Planet 999 and on Youth With You 2.

In 2020, Yaning appeared as an individual contestant on the Chinese reality survival show, Youth With You 2. She was eventually eliminated in Episode 16 with her final rank in 35th place.

In 2021, Yaning appeared as a contestant on Mnet's South Korean reality show, Girls Planet 999. In the finale, it was revealed that Yaning was unfortunately eliminated, with her rank being #12.

On April 20, 2022, Yaning made her solo debut with the mini album, Ning.
